### Get all books with price greater than 500
GET http://localhost:4004/library/Books?$filter=price gt 500

### Get all books with available copies
GET http://localhost:4004/library/Books?$filter=availableCopies gt 4

### Get books published after 2000
GET http://localhost:4004/library/Books?$filter=publishedDate gt 2000-01-01

### Get books in English
GET http://localhost:4004/library/Books?$filter=language eq 'English'

### Get books with more than 300 pages
GET http://localhost:4004/library/Books?$filter=pages gt 300

### Get active members
GET http://localhost:4004/library/Members?$filter=isActive eq true

### Get overdue borrowings
GET http://localhost:4004/library/Borrowings?$filter=status eq 'Overdue'

### Get returned borrowings
GET http://localhost:4004/library/Borrowings?$filter=status eq 'Returned'

### Get books costing between 300 and 800
GET http://localhost:4004/library/Books?$filter=price ge 300 and price le 800

### Get active authors
GET http://localhost:4004/library/Authors?$filter=isActive eq true

### 2.1 Books with "SAP" in the title (case-sensitive!)
GET http://localhost:4004/library/Books?$filter=contains(title,'CAP')

### 2.2 Books with "sap" in the title (lowercase)
GET http://localhost:4004/library/Books?$filter=contains(title,'cap')

### 2.3 Case-insensitive search for "sap"
GET http://localhost:4004/library/Books?$filter=contains(tolower(title),'cap')

### 2.4 Authors whose first name starts with "R"
GET http://localhost:4004/library/Authors?$filter=startswith(firstName,'R')

### 2.5 Books with ISBN starting with "978"
GET http://localhost:4004/library/Books?$filter=startswith(isbn,'978')

### 3.1 Books costing less than 500 and available in stock
GET http://localhost:4004/library/Books?$filter=price lt 500 and availableCopies gt 0

### 3.2 Books in English OR Hindi
GET http://localhost:4004/library/Books?$filter=language eq 'English' or language eq 'Hindi'

### 3.3 Premium books (price > 300) and more than 200 pages
GET http://localhost:4004/library/Books?$filter=price gt 300 and pages gt 200

### 3.4 Books with "CAP" in title OR price above 300
GET http://localhost:4004/library/Books?$filter=contains(title,'BTP') or price gt 300

### 3.5 Available books that are in English or Odia
GET http://localhost:4004/library/Books?$filter=availableCopies gt 0 and (language eq 'English' or language eq 'Odia')

### 4.1 All books sorted by title A-Z
GET http://localhost:4004/library/Books?$orderby=title

### 4.2 Most expensive books first
GET http://localhost:4004/library/Books?$orderby=price desc

### 4.3 Top 3 most expensive books
GET http://localhost:4004/library/Books?$orderby=price desc&$top=3

### 4.4 Cheapest 2 books
GET http://localhost:4004/library/Books?$orderby=price&$top=2

### 4.5 Page 1 (2 items per page)
GET http://localhost:4004/library/Books?$orderby=title&$top=2&$skip=0

### 4.6 Page 2 (2 items per page)
GET http://localhost:4004/library/Books?$orderby=title&$top=2&$skip=2

### 4.7 Page 3 (2 items per page)
GET http://localhost:4004/library/Books?$orderby=title&$top=2&$skip=4

### 4.8 Get total count with first page
GET http://localhost:4004/library/Books?$orderby=title&$top=2&$count=true

### 5.1 Only book titles
GET http://localhost:4004/library/Books?$select=title

### 5.2 Title and price only
GET http://localhost:4004/library/Books?$select=title,price

### 5.3 Title, price, and pages — sorted by price
GET http://localhost:4004/library/Books?$select=title,price,pages&$orderby=price

### 5.4 Member names only
GET http://localhost:4004/library/Members?$select=firstName,lastName

### 5.5 Combine $select with $filter
GET http://localhost:4004/library/Books?$select=title,price&$filter=price lt 500

### 6.1 Top 3 cheapest books with available copies — show only title and price
GET http://localhost:4004/library/Books?$filter=availableCopies gt 0&$orderby=price&$top=3&$select=title,price

### 6.2 All books sorted by language then price desc, page 1 of 2 items, with count
GET http://localhost:4004/library/Books?$orderby=language,price desc&$top=2&$skip=0&$count=true

### 6.3 Books with "CAP" in title, price 300+, sorted by price desc, only title and price
GET http://localhost:4004/library/Books?$filter=contains(title,'CAP') and price ge 300&$orderby=price desc&$sele 